{"id":149398,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/日本人拍百年前江南水乡/","date":"2011-05-02T21:30:31Z","modified":"2011-05-02T21:30:31Z","title":"日本人拍百年前江南水乡","content":"<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_50.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n南京全景</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_33.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n南门外</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_42.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n江南公园</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_4.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n仪风门，由下关进金陵之第一城门也</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_11.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n陆军小学堂</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_12.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n督练公所</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_13.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n总督衙门（张制台），现任两江总督张人骏</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_1.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n下关码头。下关在仪风门外，临长江，背狮子山，大江上下之船皆系缆于此</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_2.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n南京火车站</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_3.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n沪宁铁路火车</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_5.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n狮子山，可俯瞰长江，山上有炮台</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_6.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼓楼，结构宏壮，规模大，明时之遗迹者独此楼耳</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_7.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼓楼街</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_8.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n两江师范学堂（高等师范）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_9.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n北极阁，即明时观星台，由阁至鸡鸣寺一带丘陵是六朝台城之遗址也</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_10.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n元武湖，一名后湖，又曰蒋陵湖，周回四里，湖里有洲渚，六朝所谓昆池也。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_14.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n孝陵，在朝阳门外钟山南麓，合葬明太祖及马皇后</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_15.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n孝陵，石人石兽</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_16.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n孝陵</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_17.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n孝陵</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_18.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n钟山（紫金洞），又名紫金山、蒋山、金陵山、神烈山。<br />\n20</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_19.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n灵古寺，在孝陵之东梁开善寺遗址也</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_20.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n灵古寺</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_21.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n半山寺，宋元丰七年王安石请以所居宅舍为寺宇，赐额报宁寺。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n明故宫（西安门）</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_23.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n明故宫（午门）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_24.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n明故宫（五龙桥）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_25.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝天宫，在府城西，即古冶城遗址也，明之洪武中建，焉凡大朝贺于此习仪。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_26.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n乌龙潭</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_27.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n报恩寺（遗址），一名建初寺，又曰阿育王寺，明永乐十年敕工部重建大报恩寺造九级琉璃塔，至宣德六年凡二十九年始成，金碧照耀人天，可惜太平之乱作焦土。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_28.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n清凉山驻马坡。石头城在汉西门内清凉山，吴主孙权之古城也，驻马坡在山下龙蟠里，诸葛武侯至吴驻马以观形胜，谓“钟山龙盘，石头虎踞”即此。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_29.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n清凉山</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_30.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫愁湖胜棋楼。莫愁湖在水西门外，六朝时齐妓卢莫愁居此，故名。胜棋楼在湖上华严庵后，是明太祖与徐中山赌棋所赐。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_31.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n刘园</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_32.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n胡园</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_34.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n雨花台，在南门外，梁时有云光法师者坐山颠说法，感天雨宝花。唐卢襄名之曰“雨花台”。正学先生方孝孺墓在山腹木末亭。</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_35.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n方孝孺之墓</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_36.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n秦淮</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_37.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n秦淮（画舫及夫子庙）</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_38.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n夫子庙内殿</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_39.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n贡院孔庙，贡院在城南秦淮西北岸，考试举人之处也，其西邻为夫子庙。<br />\n40</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_40.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n贡院内部</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_41.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n贡院内部</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_43.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n燕子矶（永济子）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_44.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n燕子矶（十二洞）</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_45.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n燕子矶（十二洞）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_46.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n燕子矶</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_47.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n燕子矶</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_48.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n栖霞寺</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://himg2.huanqiu.com/attachment2010/110427/zip1303886279/1303886279_49.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n栖霞寺</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":716,"categories":[9203],"tags":[9826]}